HEADWORD: Self-repetition
<hw>Self`-rep`e*ti"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Repetition
of one's self or of one's acts; the saying or doing what one has already
said or done.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-reproach</ent>⟦br⟧
